context:
George Brown College students who have completed the Pre-Health Sciences Pathway to Advanced Diplomas and Degrees program are now eligible to enter St. George’s University (SGU) School of Medicine and Veterinary Medicine due to a new partnership between the two institutions.
 qualified students must do the following to transfer:
- Complete the Pre-Health Sciences Pathway to Advanced Diplomas and Degrees program
 Contact Information:
- Alex Irwin, Director, Transitional Education at George Brown College: 416-415-2000, ask.george@georgebrown.ca
- Chuck Furey, Director of Admissions for Canada at SGU: Not provided in the text.

Quotes from the text:
- "We are excited to partner with SGU to help our students pursue their career goals" - Alex Irwin
- "Our students will benefit greatly from the wonderful expertise across both institutions." - Chuck Furey

No specific year or number mentioned in the text.
